    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok so regarding the pH thing... what happens if i use something more alkaline like a lye wash in pretzels? does that speed things up or is it more complicated? and can u give me a more detailed breakdown of how the molecules actually interact? like how do the amino acids and sugars bond together? thanks :)",
